        <abstract> 
<p>Has read with interest GJR’s review [of Samuel Butler, <hi rend="italic">Unconscious memory</hi> (1880)] in <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> [23 (1880–1): 285–7]. Heroic of GJR to call down [Butler’s] revenge on his own head. Ernst Krause’s letter [<hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> 23 (1880–1): 288] very good.</p> 
            <p>As magistrate, CD must enforce rules regarding infection in pigs.</p>
        </abstract>
